        </p>
      </header>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-16 mb-24">
        <div class="lg:col-span-8 space-y-8 text-lg text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">

          <section class="reveal">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif font-bold text-zinc-900 mb-4">Full-Service Kitchen Remodeling — One Team, Start to Finish</h2>
            <p>
              If you're searching for <strong>"kitchen remodeling near me"</strong> in Murrieta, Temecula, or Menifee,
              you need a team that understands both the structural and aesthetic value of high-end cabinetry.
              We aren't just installers — we are <a href="/services/cabinet-maker" class="text-yellow-600 font-bold hover:underline">cabinet makers</a>
              and <a href="/services/custom-woodworking" class="text-yellow-600 font-bold hover:underline">finish carpentry specialists</a>
              who handle the design, fabrication, and installation in-house.
            </p>
            <p>
              That means your <a href="/services/custom-kitchen-cabinets" class="text-yellow-600 font-bold hover:underline">custom kitchen cabinets</a>,
              <a href="/services/granite-countertops" class="text-yellow-600 font-bold hover:underline">granite countertops</a>,
              crown molding, and trim work are all coordinated by one company. No finger-pointing between
              separate contractors. No misaligned seams between your cabinets and countertops.
              Just one team that owns the entire result.
            </p>
          </section>

          <div class="bg-zinc-50 border-l-4 border-yellow-600 p-8 my-10 reveal">
            <h4 class="text-zinc-900 font-bold mb-2">Master Cabinet Maker Pro-Tip:</h4>
            <p class="italic">"When planning a kitchen remodel in the Temecula Valley, focus on the 'Work Triangle.' By optimizing the distance between your sink, stove, and refrigerator with a custom island, you can improve kitchen efficiency by up to 30%. We design every kitchen layout around this principle."</p>
          </div>

          <section class="reveal">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif font-bold text-zinc-900 mb-4">What's Included in Our Kitchen Remodel</h2>
            <p>
              We serve luxury neighborhoods from <strong>Copper Canyon</strong> to <strong>Greer Ranch</strong>,
              and every kitchen remodel begins with an in-home consultation where we discuss your storage needs,
              workflow, and design vision.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-3 mt-4">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-yellow-600 font-bold mt-1">&#10003;</span>
                <span><strong>Custom Cabinetry</strong> — Built to the 1/16th inch from furniture-grade plywood with dovetail drawer boxes and Blum soft-close hardware. $500-$1,200+ per linear foot.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
