                <span><strong>Pantry Organization Systems</strong> — Custom pull-out shelving, spice racks, and lazy susans built from the same furniture-grade materials as your main cabinets.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-yellow-600 font-bold mt-1">&#10003;</span>
                <span><strong>Integrated Appliance Panels</strong> — Custom wood panels for refrigerators, dishwashers, and range hoods that create a seamless, built-in look.</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section class="reveal bg-zinc-50 p-8 rounded-sm border border-zinc-100">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-zinc-900 mb-6 text-center">Our Kitchen Remodel vs. Big-Box Renovation</h3>
            <div class="overflow-x-auto">
              <table class="w-full text-sm text-left">
                <thead class="border-b border-zinc-200">
                  <tr>
                    <th class="pb-4 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-zinc-600">Feature</th>
                    <th class="pb-4 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-zinc-400">Big-Box Remodel</th>
                    <th class="pb-4 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-yellow-600">First Class Kitchen Remodel</th>
                  </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody class="divide-y divide-zinc-200">
                  <tr><td class="py-4 font-bold">Cabinets</td><td class="py-4 text-zinc-500">Pre-fab particle board boxes</td><td class="py-4 font-bold text-zinc-900">Custom built to the 1/16th inch</td></tr>
                  <tr><td class="py-4 font-bold">Countertops</td><td class="py-4 text-zinc-500">Separate contractor, separate schedule</td><td class="py-4 font-bold text-zinc-900">Coordinated with cabinetry for perfect fit</td></tr>
                  <tr><td class="py-4 font-bold">Hardware</td><td class="py-4 text-zinc-500">Basic hinges, 2-3 year life</td><td class="py-4 font-bold text-zinc-900">Blum soft-close, lifetime warranty</td></tr>
                  <tr><td class="py-4 font-bold">Finish</td><td class="py-4 text-zinc-500">Paint or vinyl wrap</td><td class="py-4 font-bold text-zinc-900">Post-catalyzed conversion varnish</td></tr>
