                </tbody>
              </table>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="reveal">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif font-bold text-zinc-900 mb-4">Granite Countertops — The Perfect Pairing for Custom Cabinets</h2>
            <p>
              Every kitchen remodel we build includes <a href="/services/granite-countertops" class="text-yellow-600 font-bold hover:underline">premium countertop coordination</a>.
              We take you to the stone yard to hand-select your granite or quartz slab, then template the countertops
              after your custom cabinets are set so every edge, cutout, and seam aligns perfectly.
            </p>
            <p>
              This is the advantage of working with a <a href="/services/cabinet-maker" class="text-yellow-600 font-bold hover:underline">cabinet maker</a>
              who manages the full project — your cabinets and countertops are designed as one integrated system,
              not two separate purchases bolted together after the fact.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="reveal">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif font-bold text-zinc-900 mb-4">Our Kitchen Remodeling Process</h2>
            <div class="space-y-6 mt-6">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <span class="text-yellow-600 font-serif text-2xl font-bold">1.</span>
                <div>
                  <p class="font-bold text-zinc-900">Free In-Home Consultation</p>
                  <p>We visit your home, take laser measurements, assess your existing layout, and discuss your goals, budget, and timeline. No pressure, no commitment.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <span class="text-yellow-600 font-serif text-2xl font-bold">2.</span>
                <div>
                  <p class="font-bold text-zinc-900">3D Design & Material Selection</p>
                  <p>You see your new kitchen in full 3D before we build anything. We select wood species, stain colors, hardware finishes, and countertop materials together. You approve everything.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <span class="text-yellow-600 font-serif text-2xl font-bold">3.</span>
