                  <p class="font-bold text-zinc-900">In-Shop Cabinet Fabrication</p>
                  <p>Every cabinet is built by our craftsmen — dovetailed drawer boxes, mortise-and-tenon face frames, conversion varnish finish. All in controlled shop conditions for a perfect cure.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <span class="text-yellow-600 font-serif text-2xl font-bold">4.</span>
                <div>
                  <p class="font-bold text-zinc-900">Installation, Countertops & Finish Work</p>
                  <p>Cabinets are installed first, then countertops are templated and fabricated for a precision fit. Crown molding, trim, and final details complete the transformation. HEPA dust extraction protects your home throughout.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="reveal">
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-serif font-bold text-zinc-900 pt-10 mb-6">Kitchen Remodeling FAQ</h3>
            <div class="space-y-6">
              {faqs.map((faq) => (
                <details class="group bg-zinc-50 border border-zinc-200 rounded-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all">
                  <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer p-6 list-none">
                    <h4 class="font-serif font-bold text-zinc-800 group-hover:text-yellow-600 transition-colors pr-8">
                      {faq.question}
                    </h4>
                    <span class="text-yellow-600 transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-180 flex-shrink-0">
                      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" class="w-5 h-5">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 8.25l-7.5 7.5-7.5-7.5" />
                      </svg>
                    </span>
